journalText: I just don't feel good enough in the coding field. I am so insecure already.

I am feeling very down today. Food stamps situation that I am very stressed about. Not making enough money this month for Anna's BDay and Book Fair. Work makes me feel like I am not good enough for coding. I am tired all the time. I can't lose fat, even though I stopped drinking soda and doing yoga. I need to stop drinking but I cut back a lot. Still fat.

I have been down this week. I am stressed about food stamps, money for Anna's BDay, and bills. Plus work is been stressful. I am so insecure and feel like I suck at it. I need a second job but feel like I am not good enough to get one in my field. I don't know what to do.
